- subject: 🚗 Uber is playing the long game

---

View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/131795e2-97b4-4545-b80a-7256dc86694a/SH_Saturday_Sponsor_Banner_-_Viktor__1_.jpg?t=1778240767)
